{"tid":2149062,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"係連登識咗個男朋友呢排分咗手 決定以後拍拖前都問有無上連登...","createTime":"2020-08-10T08:18:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-10T08:59:05.000Z","uid":218575,"like":42,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"c0e5b955257d1065656bfc8fe041bbd6c10f0e76","tid":2149062,"uid":218575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T08:18:41.000Z","msg":"話說而家個男朋友係連登識 <br />\n初時傾開覺得佢幾搞笑 <br />\n個樣又白白淨 幾靚仔 <br />\n<br />\n傾咗3個月左右一齊咗<br />\n啱啱開始嘅半年都好正常<br />\n之後先發現佢癲癲地 <br />\n一嘈交就話女人都係雞係公廁<br />\n一係就就話我係連登同其他巴打flirt <br />\n又成日疑神疑鬼話我俾帽佢戴 <br />\n問佢咁而家想點就答我 感情問題一律建議分手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最撚過份係話生日<br />\n指定要去金鐘m記開生日party<br />\n食藍店都算 上連登上到佢痴撚咗線咁<br />\n以後遇到有上連登嘅人都要考慮下係咪一齊<br />\n好彩而家散咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ade630457dc108d5830fb3c041be95d1224fdb11","tid":2149062,"uid":41368,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T08:20:09.000Z","msg":"玩屎眼玩到假膠？"},{"pid":"40a4e4ceacc38a25740620ca90f6394ce4b65798","tid":2149062,"uid":183576,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T08:21:20.000Z","msg":"靜啦肥婆"},{"pid":"749e35ffca20902c01ab13526eaa46bc4f9b2631","tid":2149062,"uid":218575,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ade630457dc108d5830fb3c041be95d1224fdb11","tid":2149062,"uid":41368,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T08:20:09.000Z","msg":"玩屎眼玩到假膠？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T08:22:52.000Z","msg":"屎眼就未玩過"},{"pid":"b4d6e5126b6d0199ac2b8609102d0637dc191a13","tid":2149062,"uid":218575,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"40a4e4ceacc38a25740620ca90f6394ce4b65798","tid":2149062,"uid":183576,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T08:21:20.000Z","msg":"靜啦肥婆"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T08:23:28.000Z","msg":"搵唔到人呻 上黎連登呻下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"252f3af0fede